Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.72,0:01:37.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后又经过了72次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跨越了如此之多的失败之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:43.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于又让我遇到了机会了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.84,0:01:47.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我蔷薇少女中第一的头脑派金丝雀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:50.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要将其她的人偶狠狠教训一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用早饭的便当好好的补充一下能量吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃着这个小金特制的加糖煎蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要努力了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:07.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要开动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画画～画画～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要画出大家的样子哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.31,0:02:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画的很高兴呢  雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.43,0:02:31.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.19,0:02:35.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？苍星石在写什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.79,0:02:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在写信哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.10,0:02:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感谢爷爷和奶奶一直以来对翠星石的照料
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.80,0:02:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要说一说近来的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔？写信？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.76,0:02:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.73,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1000,0)}信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.37,0:02:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,awake…awake…awake
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:03:00.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「唤醒」的意思吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.86,0:03:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,behind…behind是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.93,0:03:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.11,0:03:12.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是「在后面」  「在后面」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.18,0:03:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…下一个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,cacophony…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.04,0:03:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…cacophony…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  「喧哗」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  那小不点人类明明也是翠星石的主人的说了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么总是和真红粘在一起！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:35.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不过我翠星石也不会在乎这种无聊小事的说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有一点点火大的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么生气了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小小…小不点莓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你你你…你在说什么的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石一点也没有嫉妒纯和真红的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:50.78,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（注：日文中「嫉妒」和「烤饼」同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.72,0:03:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对的说  就是这样的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:00.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就这样了  啊哈哈哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:05.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（白痴！白痴！白痴！）
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜呜呜…没关系的  拨弦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是煎蛋这点小事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.95,0:04:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我金丝雀是不会因此认输的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:17.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是煎蛋…不过是煎蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:22.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:23.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「吃垃圾机器」的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.97,0:04:26.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  你要用它做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.26,0:04:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是要做扫除的说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在纪不在家的时候打扫好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一定会夸奖我的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会有双花汉堡扒吃的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.13,0:04:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇——！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双  双花汉堡扒！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.33,0:04:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那样的话纯一定也会对翠星石另眼相看的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏要努力哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.30,0:04:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是的说的说的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来…这个要怎么用的说啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.45,0:05:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好  这个叫「吸尘器」的机器是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.43,0:05:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  我记得是先要这样把尾巴插好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪是这样做的说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就「隆」的一声把它弄生气哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不动的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂——你在睡觉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳！不是的  听我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.03,0:05:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！你再不马上给我起来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把你这家伙的鼻子甩断的说哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招看招看招看招看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来呀来呀来呀来呀来呀！再来一次！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么声音呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.52,0:05:41.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了！出什么事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么事都没有哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏等人什么都没有做哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.05,0:05:57.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很遗憾  大扫除作战已经失败的说了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这次一定会顺利成功的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.62,0:06:01.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名称是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.76,0:06:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午饭大作战的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.25,0:06:08.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…可是可是  纪说中午要叫外卖的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.36,0:06:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我闭嘴的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.52,0:06:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会做出温暖人心的手制料理的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.27,0:06:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饭能好吃到下巴都掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出那种超厉害的料理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.02,0:06:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让纯怦然心动的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.91,0:06:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始做的说哦  小不点小不点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.30,0:06:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉…这个可怎么办啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把鸡蛋打进去的时候加入适量调味料…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适量？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是按喜好来调味的意思的说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先加一点盐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.89,0:06:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后加黄油和榛子巧克力哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——！你在做什么的说！大笨蛋莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:47.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把软软的也放进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.82,0:06:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道一点不搭配的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.62,0:06:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这味道闻起来好像很不得了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.23,0:06:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加进去试试哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.01,0:07:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄油被乳酸菌完全的发酵了的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.21,0:07:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有点酸酸的气味哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.05,0:07:04.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我说了不能把榛子巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那种东西放进去的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.06,0:07:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大笨蛋莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:12.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…可是可是…我以为一定会好吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点莓味觉器官出问题了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就交给翠星石的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要做煮鸡蛋的说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用微波炉很简单就可以做好的说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.90,0:07:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…噗噜噗噜的煮鸡蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:37.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又怎么了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:45.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.81,0:07:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎…怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:55.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么搞的——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要生气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个是想为纯…做午饭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:06.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.72,0:08:28.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  不用这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.26,0:08:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午饭吃披萨可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.81,0:08:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.61,0:08:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下！为什么这样的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么只安慰雏莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:47.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什  什么都没有的说…什么都没有的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你干什么啊！小心我不给你午饭！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢就试试看的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我诅咒你一辈子的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我收敛一点！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.94,0:09:05.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  能不能帮忙把窗户修好？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.42,0:09:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果还是要我做吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个就给鸟或者猫吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么有种甜甜的香味？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:34.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎  煎蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不要！又要被抢走了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜呜…煎蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了哦！信写好了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.88,0:10:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点莓  你在做什么的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在等来取信的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.42,0:10:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁要过来的说？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮递员黑羊先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.92,0:10:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信是要去邮筒那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:19.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己寄出去才行的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.86,0:10:20.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮筒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.86,0:10:24.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓邮筒这种东西的说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是总是被对方的鲜血染得全身通红
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.54,0:10:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独脚站在路上  张着血盆大口的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.99,0:10:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙一到了时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:40.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被邮递员把内脏掏得四散的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邮筒担任着对寄信人予以试练的任务的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.73,0:10:47.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果寄信人是个胆小鬼的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是胆小鬼的话？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.56,0:10:58.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样  把脑袋咯吱咯吱的嚼着吃下去的说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:11:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要多加小心的说哦  小不点小不点～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪  怪物邮筒…好可怕哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就没法给纯寄信了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.88,0:11:15.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏  学苍星石的样子给纯写信了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚才没有好好的向他道谢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:22.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原  原来还有这一招的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.16,0:11:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点莓…不能小看她的说…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:49.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那个  苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.87,0:11:55.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能陪我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.18,0:12:03.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起  去寄信…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.25,0:12:06.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？消失了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:08.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有些很重要的事情和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:13.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又好像没什么事了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:16.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.68,0:12:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能被你抢先的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石要先去寄信的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下！到底是怎么一回事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔？这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:30.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话线被切断了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来  这座房子本身就是敌人的陷阱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红…真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊  现在正是关键时刻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.89,0:12:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  和我一起出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面全都是敌人的陷阱！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库库说的没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面很危险的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.85,0:12:56.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…但是但是  只出去一下下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.86,0:13:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  在这附近  不是有「那个」在徘徊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.61,0:13:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「那个」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.74,0:13:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是「那个」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.35,0:13:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:06.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫警官？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是猫！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.61,0:13:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猫…是这世上最野蛮的生物！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.81,0:13:16.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前的之前的仆从养了一只猫…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.45,0:13:18.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要——！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:38.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我连回忆都不愿意去回忆！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  对于蔷薇人偶来说  猫是敌人哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.06,0:13:43.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.79,0:13:52.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面非常危险哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.63,0:13:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏不想一个人出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.29,0:14:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:06.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:09.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然和堀江一样是人工精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.79,0:14:16.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看起来挺笨的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不招惹就不会有麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏知道哦  洗澡间里的这扇窗户总是敞开的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.79,0:14:31.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  果铃  不要这么不愿意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可是小雏的人工精灵  跟我一起来哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是小雏…只要鼓起勇气就能做到哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着饼干点心和信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.35,0:14:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出发了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用去邮筒那里寄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:50.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接交给他也可以的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.06,0:14:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前先在厕所里再检查一遍的说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵呵  又让我成功潜入了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:14:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…就如预定一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她们一个人一个人的施以血祭！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:12.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有  有点  可怕的感觉哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？怎么不关厕所的门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不清楚是怎么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看过这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:30.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不点人类就会被翠星石的魅力击倒的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.80,0:15:32.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（纯先生收）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.12,0:15:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你想做什么的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉悟了吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.77,0:15:52.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太过分了的说！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.36,0:15:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石拼了命才写出来的重要的信…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？这出乎我预料之外了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.92,0:16:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶！竟敢把充满我翠星石的真诚心意的信…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷  冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.64,0:16:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是出了一点小错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无益！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.35,0:16:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这么吵啊  又是雏莓那家伙吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:16.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  跑到哪里去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道这样  不出来就好了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜…绕一点路吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.19,0:17:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼…吓死我了  不过一点都不疼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  是猫啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.48,0:17:23.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了「外面很危险不要出去」之后就没管她…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:30.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有找到她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会一个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:44.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  猫先生  真的吗  邮筒真的在这边吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.27,0:17:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.81,0:17:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要想吃饼干的话尽管说  我还有呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:19.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么把我丢下了  真过分哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:27.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.08,0:18:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.98,0:18:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:36.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓那家伙  到底去哪里了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.93,0:18:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  出什么事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:43.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我来拿订下的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.99,0:18:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是的是的  已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  请请请  请这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红色的…独脚…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…这就是邮筒吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:19:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胆…胆小鬼会被它用那张大嘴咯吱咯吱…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可  可是  我要给纯寄信哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以哭哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.11,0:19:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给纯寄信哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够  够不着呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:27.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会放弃的…绝对不会放弃的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:31.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要给纯寄信的！一定要寄去哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏…小雏！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.84,0:19:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雏要寄信哦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:48.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差…一…一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.28,0:19:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过…已经…不行了哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴…巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.82,0:20:16.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴  你为什么一直微笑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.94,0:20:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？我在微笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！看起来很高兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.16,0:20:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我是很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为雏莓啊  你终于改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变了？因为改变了  所以高兴？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.01,0:20:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前总是在撒娇的雏莓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.16,0:20:40.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人这样努力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓  你喜欢樱田同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢！也喜欢巴和纪！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:50.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有真红她们  我都最喜欢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:54.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  不要让他们担心了  快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.77,0:20:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雏莓！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是纯哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.72,0:21:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  有点吃惊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.77,0:21:11.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人是一个男孩子呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.18,0:21:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做纯吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.35,0:21:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金  抬起头来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.09,0:21:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抬——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真稀罕呢  男孩子竟然会对人偶感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  人偶是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此的～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此～可爱啊～这件衣服超可爱的呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.58,0:21:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想要其她的蔷薇少女啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.32,0:21:44.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小小美  再这样会因为摩擦生热烧起来的～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.07,0:21:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.25,0:21:49.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:51.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.51,0:21:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～梦幻的蔷薇少女系列
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.70,0:21:49.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能得到其她人偶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.04,0:21:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要多么辛苦的加班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.90,0:21:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要去兼职的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:21:57.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯  有信寄给你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.47,0:22:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？这是哪里的推销信啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:02.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么都看不明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.39,0:22:04.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字写得丑到家了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.19,0:22:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有脸寄出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.35,0:23:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红？真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.13,0:23:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍星石  看到真红了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.52,0:23:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才在那边喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:50.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你还是别过去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.99,0:23:52.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？为什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.88,0:23:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她好像回想起了痛苦的往事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦的往事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:23:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想  应该是那个时候的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一起经历过的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  蔷薇少女  梦见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.45,0:24:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如梦中所见
